ca.uwaterloo.softeng.advisor

Class Audit

  • java.lang.Object
    • ca.uwaterloo.softeng.advisor.Audit

  •  class Audit
extends java.lang.Object
    Audit class audits a student for a given plan. The status of the audit can be retrieved along with a list of courses matching each requirement.
